00:53:36.649 --> 00:53:39.690
e gjithe keto gjera.

00:53:45.565 --> 00:53:48.399
Tani ata qe jane ne anen emocionale

00:53:48.774 --> 00:53:52.024
shohin egon e te tjereve, ndersa ata qe jane ne anen e egos

00:53:52.441 --> 00:53:55.732
